Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.79,0:08:17.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且還嫌我煩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.53,0:08:19.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.12,0:08:22.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 昨天謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.41,0:08:24.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fscy75\fscx80\b1}沒{\r}影響到你美術部的活動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.76,0:08:28.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 野崎君竟然知道我是哪個部的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.22,0:08:31.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因{\fscy80\fscx80\b1}為{\r}我一直在關注著你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.34,0:08:33.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關…關注是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.74,0:08:38.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能畫出那種基本不出框的海報的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.33,0:08:41.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹出的活也一定很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.80,0:08:44.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是看上了我的技術！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.27,0:08:52.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然很厲害啊 佐倉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.03,0:08:57.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多虧你 這次可以在截稿日期前交上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.08,0:08:59.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 野崎君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.64,0:09:02.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你偶爾會傷痕累累的去學校
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.10,0:09:04.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 野崎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.37,0:09:05.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fscy75\fscx80\b1}沒{\r}事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.13,0:09:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生了什{\fscy75\fscx80}麼{\r}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.75,0:09:07.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}怎{\fscy75\fscx80}麼{\r}全是傷\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.54,0:09:08.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心情好像很不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.46,0:09:13.83,note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(166,169)\fs32\frz3}濕布 腱鞘炎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.96,0:09:13.83,note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(140,400)}濕布 肩周炎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.73,0:09:13.83,note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(1080,344)}睡眠不足
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.41,0:09:13.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個是因{\fscy75\fscx80}麼{\r}截稿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.16,0:09:18.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還以{\fscy80\fscx80\b1}為{\r}是打架或者暗地裡當黑道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.13,0:09:21.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,專門攻擊頸部的不良少年嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.50,0:09:23.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真恐怖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.50,0:09:25.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是表面是一般人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.50,0:09:28.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,背地裡是不良少年 算是王道設定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.49,0:09:31.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個能當NETA用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.19,0:09:34.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會在背地裡抽煙喝酒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.81,0:09:36.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 因{\fscy80\fscx80\b1}為{\r}是少女漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.60,0:09:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fscy80\fscx80\b1}為{\r}了健全 煙{\fscy75\fscx80}換{\r}{\fscy80\fscx80\b1}為{\r}巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.45,0:09:41.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,酒就{\fscy75\fscx80}換{\r}成果汁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.49,0:09:43.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 這行不通啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.49,0:09:46.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是漫畫 違反法律也是會被罵的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.52,0:09:49.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 這{\fscy75\fscx80}麼{\r}麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.01,0:09:53.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 這個難道是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.84,0:09:56.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傳統的心跳情節發生的前奏嗎 夢野老師
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.48,0:10:00.18,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能 能和你一起回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.98,0:10:02.31,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是我騎自行車啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.94,0:10:04.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 你在{\fscy80\fscx75}說{\r}什{\fscy75\fscx80}麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.12,0:10:06.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什{\fscy75\fscx80}麼{\r} 就是自行車啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.65,0:10:09.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在後座感受到的他的體溫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.48,0:10:11.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扶在哪裡好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.18,0:10:14.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手在抖 心在跳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.84,0:10:17.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在這個是違反道路交通法的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.72,0:10:19.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.57,0:10:22.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這個自行車不能載人的時代
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.43,0:10:26.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想和騎自行車的他一起回家的辦法 就只有這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.38,0:10:31.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺不夠華麗 也{\fscy75\fscx80\b1}沒{\r}辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.30,0:10:33.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.40,0:10:35.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渣男啊 這個人 太渣了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.62,0:10:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.81,0:10:38.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 有種遛馬的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.16,0:10:46.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考慮少女漫畫的故事情節 真的是好辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.27,0:10:54.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐倉 要一起回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.63,0:10:56.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要一起回 要的 要的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.45,0:10:57.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是騎自行車來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.67,0:10:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你坐在後面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.91,0:11:09.95,title2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(985,593)}月刊少女野崎君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.91,0:11:09.95,logo,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(988,681)\c&HFFFBFF&}異域字幕組{\fs18\b1}>▽<{\fs28}作死病院
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.95,0:11:14.95,title2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(177,170)}月刊少女野崎君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.95,0:11:14.95,logo,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFBFF&\pos(178,259)}異域字幕組{\fs18\b1}>▽<{\fs28}作死病院
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.32,0:11:34.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎 怎{\fscy75\fscx80}麼{\r}回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.00,0:11:40.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野崎君 難道是因{\fscy80\fscx80\b1}為{\r} 昨天我{\fscy80\fscx75}說{\r}很憧憬這個就勉強……
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.72,0:11:44.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎{\fscy75\fscx80}麼{\r}辦 開始緊張了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.33,0:11:47.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話{\fscy80\fscx75}說{\r}回來 自行車後座應該怎{\fscy75\fscx80}麼{\r}坐來著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.82,0:11:50.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣？這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.81,0:11:57.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有{\fscy75\fscx80\b1}沒{\r}有後座的情況 那種時候 這樣可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.12,0:12:03.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要知道有這種事 我就會提前練習一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.68,0:12:04.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐倉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.69,0:12:05.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.32,0:12:07.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.87,0:12:09.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我一起騎 然後把感想告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.24,0:12:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雙人自行車
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.66,0:12:14.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩人合騎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.92,0:12:30.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺如何
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.63,0:12:33.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有點兜風的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.97,0:12:36.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 接下來要右轉彎了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.42,0:12:36.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.66,0:12:42.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下個拐角要轉彎了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.31,0:12:42.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.60,0:13:03.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你感覺到愛的降臨了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.18,0:13:07.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是好像產生了…一股信賴感
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.31,0:13:10.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.69,0:13:13.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是後座的人不該蹬腳踏板啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.19,0:13:16.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此 那我就這{\fscy75\fscx80}麼{\r}坐著試試
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.83,0:13:28.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己一點都不出力的罪惡感 實在太強烈了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.82,0:13:30.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我也蹬一下吧！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.07,0:13:37.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你至少要用手摟住我的腰 來嘗試一下心跳加速的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.73,0:13:56.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之 我根據今天的經驗試著畫出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.27,0:13:57.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得怎{\fscy75\fscx80}麼{\r}樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.24,0:14:01.04,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不嫌棄的話 要不要搭我的車呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.04,0:14:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,土掉渣了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.96,0:14:05.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐倉 怎{\fscy75\fscx80}麼{\r}了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:07.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fscy75\fscx80\b1}沒{\r}啥 總覺得這種...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.06,0:14:10.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全感受不到主人公會受歡迎的因素
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.54,0:14:14.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 受歡迎的因素啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.61,0:14:19.72,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只有先到的三名才能坐在我後面呦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.13,0:14:21.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四人自行車？！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.57,0:14:24.09,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}閃開 今天我一定要做這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.29,0:14:27.20,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fscy75\fscx80\b1}別{\r}開玩笑了 這個座位是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.16,0:14:31.61,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我{\fscy80\fscx80\b1}為{\r}你 特地預留下了第二個車座
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.20,0:14:32.75,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是專座喲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.77,0:14:34.43,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.16,0:14:39.03,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}除了我之外 還有好多的人坐過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.38,0:14:40.40,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我討厭這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.70,0:14:42.26,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不行...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.81,0:14:45.28,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明明知道{\fscy80\fscx75}說{\r}了這{\fscy75\fscx80}麼{\r}任性的話 是會被他討厭的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.55,0:14:46.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.27,0:14:48.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後會變成什{\fscy75\fscx80}麼{\r}樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.13,0:14:51.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,車座全都被偷了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.36,0:15:01.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是最後 雜誌社的編輯覺得太過惡搞給駁回了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.50,0:15:03.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最終變成了這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.12,0:15:06.50,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你...你先回去也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.90,0:15:09.13,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 太晚了就讓我送你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.03,0:15:11.35,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而且這樣一起走的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.05,0:15:13.86,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然只有一點 能和你在一起的時間變長了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.48,0:15:18.96,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果時間能夠就這樣停止該多好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.49,0:15:23.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一期也好精彩呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.50,0:15:24.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夢野老師的「來戀愛吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.36,0:15:27.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自行車那裡的情節 真的好帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.09,0:15:28.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧 佐倉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.07,0:15:31.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.31,0:15:42.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey 野崎君 要不要來坐？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.55,0:15:43.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可是你的特等席呦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.68,0:15:46.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey～HeyHey 野崎君！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.91,0:15:47.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貌似很中意這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.32,0:16:00.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 雖{\fscy80\fscx75}說{\r}過程很曲折
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.52,0:16:03.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但最終還是變成了一篇浪漫的少女漫畫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.87,0:16:05.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.56,0:16:10.53,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好想就這樣一直被你緊緊的抱著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.44,0:16:14.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也是野崎君想的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.06,0:16:18.90,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不可以 {\fscy80\fscx80\b1}為{\r}什{\fscy75\fscx80}麼{\r}我總是在想鈴木君的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.40,0:16:21.51,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好討厭討厭討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.74,0:16:25.22,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}佔據我心裡每一處的鈴木君...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.89,0:16:27.91,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}最討厭了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.06,0:16:31.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這...這也是野崎君...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.93,0:16:33.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐倉 怎{\fscy75\fscx80}麼{\r}了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.71,0:16:35.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 {\fscy75\fscx80\b1}沒{\r}什{\fscy75\fscx80}麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.05,0:16:38.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野崎君{\fscy80\fscx80\b1}為{\r}什{\fscy75\fscx80}麼{\r}要畫少女漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.55,0:16:42.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對此很有興趣 所以就這樣順其自然地...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.54,0:16:46.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然這{\fscy75\fscx80}麼{\r}{\fscy80\fscx75}說{\r} 但卻畫出了這樣的{\fscy80\fscx80\b1}內{\r}容
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.33,0:16:47.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果換成我就絕對畫不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.66,0:16:50.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是戀愛經驗的差距吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.44,0:16:53.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也{\fscy75\fscx80\b1}沒{\r}什{\fscy75\fscx80}麼{\r}好著急的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.77,0:16:57.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看我 可是連初戀都還{\fscy75\fscx80\b1}沒{\r}經歷過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.60,0:16:59.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你到底{\fscy80\fscx80\b1}為{\r}什{\fscy75\fscx80}麼{\r}會在畫少女漫畫啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.43,0:17:03.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  倒是不少人來找我做戀愛諮詢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.80,0:17:06.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐倉你有喜歡的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.80,0:17:08.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 我...我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.78,0:17:14.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那...那個 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.40,0:17:21.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最初是被他的身高 和他具有男子氣概的個性所吸引
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:24.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟他告白過...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.32,0:17:25.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他{\fscy75\fscx80\b1}沒{\r}有明白我的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.87,0:17:31.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 也因此我們{\fscy80\fscx75}說{\r}話的機會多了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.82,0:17:35.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他貌似只把我當做了萬能小助手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.50,0:17:38.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種傢伙究竟哪裡好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.06,0:18:13.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 就這{\fscy75\fscx80}麼{\r}下去好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.76,0:18:35.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕 青木會怒的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.90,0:18:36.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.75,0:19:01.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野崎君！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.34,0:19:41.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fscy75\fscx80\b1}沒{\r}錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.74,0:19:43.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.40,0:19:49.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還{\fscy75\fscx80\b1}沒{\r}有把自己的心意 傳達出去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.76,0:19:55.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再向他好好地告白一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.77,0:19:58.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野崎君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.04,0:20:01.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是佐倉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.56,0:20:04.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千代 加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.68,0:20:05.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是第二次了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.90,0:20:08.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須好好地 把自己的心意告訴他才行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.82,0:20:13.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什{\fscy75\fscx80}麼{\r}事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.56,0:20:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.89,0:20:19.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.44,0:20:25.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…那…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.25,0:20:30.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.31,0:20:38.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.92,0:20:50.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是你的忠實粉！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.55,0:20:52.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂的 我懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.29,0:20:55.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.06,0:21:00.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萬歲…（┬＿┬）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.12,0:21:04.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真高興呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.81,0:21:06.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是第二張簽名啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.24,0:21:09.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萬歲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.67,0:21:12.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萬歲…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.25,0:21:18.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是個白癡啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.81,0:22:56.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐倉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.30,0:22:59.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野崎君
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.70,0:23:01.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天禦子柴也會來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.32,0:23:03.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是個男生 你{\fscy75\fscx80\b1}沒{\r}問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.17,0:23:06.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禦子柴？是個什{\fscy75\fscx80}麼{\r}樣的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.16,0:23:08.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是個堅強卻很容易受傷的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.04,0:23:10.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很敏感的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.11,0:23:13.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在心裡都是叫他「小禦禦」來著
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.25,0:23:17.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想必是個治癒系的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.42,0:23:19.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早啊 野崎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.94,0:23:34.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？那邊的小矮子是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.62,0:23:36.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這位是 禦子柴君
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.48,0:23:38.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你個大騙子！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.90,0:23:40.90,note2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H27D68E&\fs48\pos(920,670)}創刊號     完結
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.61,0:23:43.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 這裡刊登了夢野老師的留言
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.02,0:23:47.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前兩天被學校的朋友要簽名了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.39,0:23:48.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我緊張到連筆都拿不穩了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.11,0:23:50.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是拿到簽名她能很開心就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.63,0:23:52.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今後我也會心意滿滿地加倍努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.29,0:23:55.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一話 新女主角參上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.28,0:23:55.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要來看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
